Rating: 1
The REAL recipe - Boil oxtail in a large pot. Spoon all the scum out. - Drain all the water out and wash the oxtail bones. Fill your pot with cold water and place the bones back in the pot. Bring to a boil. - Add 2 3-inch long pieces of peeled daikon, palm sized piece of ginger and 1 medium onion, 2 star anise, 1 stick cinnamon, 3 cardamon pods. - Simmer 2 hours. Add 3 1 1/2 inch pieces of rock sugar and salt to taste. Remove the bones, veggies and spices. NEVER, NEVER, NEVER serve with lettuce!

