A nice enough Americanized version. I'll make it when I'm too lazy to make the real thing. The comment from the Vietnamese reviewer is correct, any Vietnamese guests would be horrified by the lettuce. Two comments: that is way two much cloves, maybe 1/2t at most, and bean thread is so NO WAY! for this dish. It is served with rice noodles (the flat kind of whatever width, not round ones). Chicken is also nice, cook in broth and shred.

